{
  "name": "Cyclone (reaction)",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/air/wind-tornado-cyclone-white.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Can only be cast on an ally within range as a Reaction when that ally is attacked. Ally may voluntarily fail the following versus test.</p><hr /><p>Triggers a vs test of caster's Will + {{math spellPower \"*\" 3}} against target's Strength/Dexterity Test.</p><hr /><p>On success, the target is trapped in the cyclone for up to three rounds, unable to act. While trapped, they cannot be harmed by Physical attacks or direct Magic (e.g. projectiles, beams) and can be moved one hex per round. <br /><br />Effects of this spell are not automated and must be resolved manually.<br />Apply effect to get a duration counter.</p>",
